The `v0.4` API is layered:
the Core API is the foundation layer offering a scalable, event-driven actor framework for creating agentic workflows;
the AgentChat API is built on Core, offering a task-driven, high-level framework for building interactive agentic applications. It is a replacement for AutoGen `v0.2` .

